    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Visit the French National Assembly from home!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely explore the National Assembly and the Hôtel de Lassay using your computer, Steam Deck, or virtual reality headset, in a fully immersive experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A place of exceptional heritage and history</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wander at your own pace through the iconic spaces of the National Assembly — the chamber, the library, the reception rooms, and the gardens — with smooth and intuitive navigation. Discover areas rarely open to the public, such as the Hôtel de Lassay, the official residence of the President of the National Assembly.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An interactive tour</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with artworks, paintings, and statues to access detailed information about each piece. Follow the guided tour in the chamber, or explore freely to learn more about the symbols, institutions, and heritage of the French Republic.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A shared experience with friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks to multiplayer mode, visit the National Assembly and the Hôtel de Lassay together, online or via local network. Enjoy a collective journey with friends or in a group.</p>",
